name: Paw Master the Jumpy Brown Puppy
name_original: Paw Master the Jumpy Brown Puppy
description:
Absolutely FREE and super fun game!

Pole vault from land to land
Avoid the mean birds
Do not jump on the bombs
Catch the parrot and get an extra life!

Compete with your FRIENDS and beat the world record! Maybe you will be on the top of the leaderboard!
The brown Puppy is waiting for you! Be the pro of Paw Master the Jumpy Puppy!
